{"tid":1502360,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無葵芳人最近都出現皮膚問題？","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T16:17:18.000Z","uid":311513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"24993b749c0b2bd4ddf6ddd3ce8dd9631773a821","tid":1502360,"uid":311513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"唔知係我心邪定咩，我係葵芳返工，搭巴士要經過狗鐵站<br />\n8月6號開始手生左一粒水泡<br />\n初時無為意<br />\n跟住開始慢慢生一粒粒好細既紅點，好痕<br />\n唔知係咪d有機氣體搞到咁定係我自己比野咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為奇就奇在d紅點係主要生係衫蓋住既位，手臂又無乜事<br />\n利申：我日日有沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且平時無皮膚問題<br />\n<br />\n講返d比較易信服既野<br />\n我有d同事本身有濕疹，呢幾日都突然發作，有位同事嚴重到d濕疹生係關節位痛到佢行唔到路，上埋頸同面，要sick leave<br />\n佢話以前唔會咁嚴重，最近都無亂食野<br />\n醫生問佢有無去d有催淚氣體既場所<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話自己係葵芳返工<br />\n醫生就話可能因為日日經過先咁嚴重，建議佢避免經過狗鐵站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家搽左藥就無咁痛lu<br />\n<br />\n如果係我個人唔衛生比野咬，我就去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果都有其他人係咁，咁我就接受我又無左幾年命呢個事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab20f478d51aaae79a735299fea70ec8e6bef9d","tid":1502360,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早日康復<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa671fa657a6e9f411ca769deca30a63033b3021","tid":1502360,"uid":311513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:57:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5c5d1d4588e611b87ecf1650c42c1c3aab0f78f9","tid":1502360,"uid":21788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:03:22.000Z","msg":"我都係葵芳返工 <br />\n唔知係咪真係催淚彈嘅殘留物搞到我膝頭位有紅點<br />\n本身以為自己皮膚過敏先有<br />\n後來俾你講下先醒起係差佬站內射完先咁<br />\n而家仲搽緊藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b123998481f6e4cc201667b7138e016615c5b41","tid":1502360,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"D 催淚好似講到話有過量山唉在入面。小心。<br />\n或看看需不需要睇醫生"},{"pid":"f47ff2961bb08295be489e1c2b8531d5b477a6e6","tid":1502360,"uid":311513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c5d1d4588e611b87ecf1650c42c1c3aab0f78f9","tid":1502360,"uid":21788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:03:22.000Z","msg":"我都係葵芳返工 <br />\n唔知係咪真係催淚彈嘅殘留物搞到我膝頭位有紅點<br />\n本身以為自己皮膚過敏先有<br />\n後來俾你講下先醒起係差佬站內射完先咁<br />\n而家仲搽緊藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:51:15.000Z","msg":"小心為上啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a933b393803db6abb1b46579a469fb5d6a1b1d1","tid":1502360,"uid":311513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b123998481f6e4cc201667b7138e016615c5b41","tid":1502360,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"D 催淚好似講到話有過量山唉在入面。小心。<br />\n或看看需不需要睇醫生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"遲d如果無好轉會睇醫生<br />\n扮曬野call sick先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfeb5353e936237b12350e12d8ec039fa3822873","tid":1502360,"uid":312358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"我都係日日喺葵芳搭地鐵有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔係紅點 係突然紅色一撻撻好痕<br />\n係手掌手臂嘅外露位有事咋 (只著短袖長褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"}]}